Module HunterPaceTimes
Package Classes

Class Team

java.lang.Object
Classes.Team
public class Team
extends java.lang.Object
An object containing data pertaining to a specific team.

The excluded identifier marks whether or not the team should be included in the final scores. If it is set to true, then the team will not show up on any final scores by default.

    • isDivision

      public boolean isDivision​(Division division)
      Returns whether or not the Team is categorized under the given Division

      This method compares the names without case restrictions, so if the Team had it's division set as "HUnt", this method will return true if asked to compare it to a Division named "hunt".

      Parameters:
      division - Division to check if the Team is part of it
      Returns:
      True if the team falls under the given Division, and False if it does not.
      See Also:
      Division
